text: "What Have You Done for Me Lately" is a 1986 song by Janet Jackson and is the leading single from her third studio album Control. It went to number 4 in the United States, number 3 in the United Kingdom and the Netherlands, number 1 in Zimbabwe, number 27 in New Zealand, number 6 in Canada and Australia and number 10 in Ireland. ==Track listings== *Australian / US and Canadian 7-inch single :A.
